Thing is...
Darius is difficult to build against, if you try to go armor, he has innate penetration.
Going MR to weaken the bleed just makes him kill you with other attacks
If he goes tanky, he STILL has the armor penetration to keep him deadly.
And ffs, his kit is PERFECTLY designed to ignore build paths vs him, and unless he messes up on his ult (rarely happens) he becomes unstoppable because he can farm with massive waveclear...
Let's narrow this down some shall we?
